ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectOrder Amending the Order Imposing a Surtax on the Importation of Certain Steel Goods (Exclusions)
PrecisOrder amending the ORDER IMPOSING A SURTAX ON THE IMPORTATION OF CERTAIN STEEL GOODS (EXCLUSIONS) in order to exclude certain products, as recommended by the Canadian International Trade Tribunal, as a result of its exclusion inquiry, from the application of safeguard measures, considering that they are not available in Canada. The product exclusions refer to certain dimensions, grades, technical specifications or end-uses for heavy plate and stainless steel wire.
